The Made In Nova Scotia Store





















































 








































Select Page


  
 



 



 










 
 



Treasures From Across the Province!
Located at 324 Main Street, Antigonish, the Made In Nova Scotia Store carries a wide selection of goods from throughout Eastern Nova Scotia and the rest of the province. Everything in the store has been crafted by provincial artisans, craftspeople, artists, and bakers. Our selection changes every week so pop by – you’ll never know what new treasure you’ll find!
Open today from 10:00am to 5:00pm

 
 



 
 


The Made In Nova Scotia Store
 
 


A Little Shop of Big Treasures…
All of the products we carry have been made right here in the province. From the practical to the whimsical, you’ll find the perfect gift for that special someone, a great accent for your home decor, or even some of the tastiest snacks around!

 

 

Be sure to stop in and see us across from Shoppers Drug Mart in Antigonish, Nova Scotia as we continue to introduce new products and vendors to the area.

 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 



























